                     But the Earth here meant is a diuine, spirituall,
immortall nature; called Earth by a Metaphor,
incapable of suffering terrene fragilitie. This is
Gods Earth, and that in a high and mysticall
sense, though proper enough. Indeed Domini
terra, the earth is the Lords and the fulnes
